    "FindSuitableK(Xs, log 2 (N), log 2 (M), δ) → K: given given Xs the secret distribution, log 2 (N) and log 2 (M) and δ, returns K such that Pr [∥I(Y)∥ > K]) ≤ 2 δ.",
